title: Dennis J.
text: Tried other "on line" stores, some are ok some seem like catolog stores that are out of stock on common parts(brake pads,fork seals,airfilter). granted my bike is 31 years old,but low miles and very fast when needed. Sport bike track gear had it all instock with free shipping and great product descriptions and fitament on everything I viewed on the web site.
